 calf stretch","durationSec":40,"description":"Lengthen the calf and Achilles.","cues":["straight back leg","heel down"]}],"targetsJoints":["right_hip","left_ankle","right_shoulder"],"notes":"Do this on training days before skill work."},{"id":"tennis-forehand-strength","title":"Corrective strength","focus":"Build strength where your mechanics differ most from the pro.","durationMin":20,"difficulty":"advanced","equipment":["dumbbells","cable or band","bench"],"warmup":[{"name":"Dynamic full-body warm-up","durationSec":300,"description":"Light cardio plus the mobility drills above.","cues":["raise heart rate","move through range"]}],"main":[{"name":"Romanian deadlift","sets":3,"reps":"8-10","description":"Train the hip hinge and posterior chain.","cues":["push hips back","flat back"]},{"name":"Single-leg calf raise","sets":3,"reps":"12-15","description":"Strengthen the calf and stabilize the ankle.","cues":["full height","balance"]},{"name":"Landmine press","sets":3,"reps":"8-10","description":"Build stable overhead pressing strength.","cues":["ribs down","full press"]}],"cooldown":[{"name":"Couch stretch","durationSec":45,"description":"Open the hip flexors of each leg.","cues":["squeeze glute","tall"]},{"name":"Wall calf stretch","durationSec":40,"description":"Lengthen the calf and Achilles.","cues":["straight back leg","heel down"]}],"targetsJoints":["right_hip","left_ankle","right_shoulder"],"notes":"2–3× per week with a day of recovery between sessions."},{"id":"tennis-forehand-skill","title":"Skill & sequencing","focus":"Transfer the corrections into your tennis forehand.","durationMin":23,"difficulty":"advanced","equipment":["medicine ball","your normal gear"],"warmup":[{"name":"Shadow reps","durationSec":180,"description":"Slow-motion Forehand reps focusing on the cues.","cues":["load the outside hip, then drive up","firm ankle at contact","make a bigger arc"]}],"main":[{"name":"Loaded open-stance drives — coil onto the back hip and explode up into contact",